label: Country
definition: Country in which study was conducted

label: Sample mean Schistosoma mansoni eggs per gram by microscopy
definition: Average eggs per gram (epg) of S.mansoni for all recorded observations
codebookDescription: Eggs per gram (epg) of S. mansoni eggs from all available Kato-Katz (KK) tests for the participant

label: Schistosoma haematobium (per 10 ml), by microscopy
definition: Mean Schistosoma haematobium eggs counted on all filtrations of the urine sample
codebookDescription: Eggs per gram (epg) of S. haematobium eggs from all available urine filtrations for the participant

label: Schistosoma mansoni, by microscopy
definition: Binary flag to indicate S.mansoni infection through egg detection in Kato-Katz test
codebookDescription: Binary flag to indicate S. mansoni infection through egg detection in KK

label: Schistosoma haematobium, by microscopy
definition: Presence or absence of Schistosoma haematobium infection in this study participant, based on detection of at least one egg in the urine sample.
codebookDescription: Binary flag to indicate S. haematobium infection through egg detection in urine

label: Schistosoma mansoni infection, by CCA
definition: Binary flag to indicate S.mansoni infection through CCA
codebookDescription: Binary flag to indicate positive CCA test for S. mansoni

label: Hemastix test results
definition: Binary flag to indicate positive hemastix test
codebookDescription: Binary flag to indicate positive hemastix test
